      "instruction": "<p>Once done, remove the <strong>baked</strong> <strong>sweet potato</strong> from the oven and carefully slice in half lengthways</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
